concepts.term: predictive and personalized role in medicine

evidence: We discussed advances in CT technology, covering both hardware improvements and algorithmic innovations.
We also looked at how imaging can play a more predictive and personalized role in medicine.
The meeting is structured into many symposiums running in parallel.
We had our session, shared our work, exchanged ideas, and learned from other fields.
